<section class="home-page-signed-out">
  <div class="title-logo row">
    <div class="twelve columns">
      <h1>HabitMi</h1>
      <p>
        Get a head start to creating lasting habits and become the best you!
      </p>
      <%= link_to 'Join Today', new_user_registration_path, class: 'button' %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="explanation-carousel container">
    <div class="row icons">
      <div class="three columns active">
        <a href="#" class="icon-link our-mission">
          <%= fa_icon 'file-text-o 3x' %>
          <p>Our Mission</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="three columns">
        <a href="#" class="icon-link trending-goals">
          <%= fa_icon 'heart 3x' %>
          <p>Trending Goals</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="three columns">
        <a href="#" class="icon-link how-to-habit-mi">
          <%= fa_icon 'calendar 3x' %>
          <p>How to HabitMi</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="three columns">
        <a href="#" class="icon-link win-prizes">
          <%= fa_icon 'gift 3x' %>
          <p>Win Prizes</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="explanations our-mission row active">
      <div class="twelve columns">
        <h1>Our Mission</h1>
        <p>
          Have you ever set a goal and then lacked the motivation to follow
          through?
        </p>
        <p>Well, we have too.</p>
        <p>
          Sometimes that Game of Thrones episode is so much more tempting than
          diving back into the Python course on Codeacademy, and the tray of
          free cupcakes in the staff room seems to be calling out to you
          much more than the salad bowl beside it.
        </p>
        <p>
          HabitMi is here to change that. Our mission is to turn the goal
          you want to achieve into habit, so that it wonâ€™t seem like
          something you have to force yourself to do.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="explanations trending-goals row">
      <div class="twelve columns">
        <h1>Trending Goals</h1>
        <ol>
          <li>
            Learn new skill
            <ul>
              <li>Learn to speak another language</li>
              <li>Coding</li>
              <li>Learning how to play an instrument</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
            Exercise
            <ul>
              <li>Lose weight</li>
              <li>Be healthy</li>
              <li>Improve performance</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
            New Diet
            <ul>
              <li>Lose weight</li>
              <li>Paleo Diet</li>
              <li>Vegetarian Diet</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>Being on time</li>
          <li>Studying</li>
          <li>
            Self-improvement
            <ul>
              <li>Write in a journal</li>
              <li>Saying Thank You</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="explanations how-to-habit-mi row">
      <div class="twelve columns">
        <h1>How To HabitMi</h1>
        <ul>
          <li>Pick an existing category/goal or create your own</li>
          <li>Find 5 friends (or strangers) to achieve it together</li>
          <li>Log your activity everyday and earn points</li>
          <li>Be the leader in the group with most points</li>
          <li>Congratulate yourself on your way to being a superhuman</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="explanations win-prizes row">
      <div class="twelve columns">
        <h1>Win Prizes</h1>
